description: Thai Thai is out on the streets cooking up gourmet Thai food for the Bay area. We use only the freshest ingredients from Thailand, like clean and fresh choice meats, organic veggies, and the highest quality produce so our dishes are super fresh and super tasty. Our recipes have been passed down from generation to generation, and we don't use any MSG to achieve that authentic Thai flavor!We have 5 regular menu which is Pad Thai, Sweet Basil, Red Curry, Yellow Curry, and Thai Thai Chicken. Also, we have Thai dessert, Thai appetizers, and Thai drinks. We also have more than 30 rotational menu items that will change everyday such us Pad Kee Mao, Pad See Ew, Green Curry, and Pineapple Fried Rice. You'll keep coming back for more!
name: Thai Thai
